                   class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 underline">
                    Philosophy
                </a>
                &mdash; the design rules the project operates under.
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/about/changelog"
                   class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 underline">
                    Changelog
                </a>
                &mdash; what has shipped per session, from v0.1 onward.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-10 text-sm">
            <a href="/" class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-900 underline">
                &larr; Home
            </a>
        </p>

